{"tid":727550,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿恩火滾：如果尼馬想瞓低 不如上床瞓！","createTime":"2018-07-03T06:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T15:29:30.000Z","uid":147522,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"389c7597836efebcb94ae1d2212eebf87b7e8280","tid":727550,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"在世界盃16強墨西哥0：2不敵巴西一仗，拿恩跟尼馬出現爭議性畫面，後者的反應令這位後衛直斥「想瞓低不如返上床」。<br />\n<br />\n下半場時有次尼馬倒在邊線，拿恩再疑似踏到他的腳踝，尼馬馬上在地上滾，不過該巴西球星之後又好似沒有受傷繼續比賽。拿恩不禁表示：「這是足球，如果他不想被碰到，就應該參與其他運動。他這樣想躺下，不如回家睡覺。他倒下，我碰他是因為想找波，我知道他有才華，但也知道他的把戲。」<br />\n<br />\n拿恩續說：「尼馬十分有才華，但如果他可以花多點心思踢波，而非在其他東西上，會更出色。或者他擔心，所以這是他減壓的方式吧。」"},{"pid":"49ec53441c28904b53cca4fca2c3251790550e75","tid":727550,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"如果想仆街 為什麼需要忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455aa68a68460cd89fe378fdbf6ed13b125229f1","tid":727550,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"雖然拉恩唔知點解抽左佢一下水<br />\n<br />\n但唔係以為咁大反應對方就會食黃下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429ab0eb6a59b3066ff603cdd5a95fe588996f94","tid":727550,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"馬爻口吾至刂"},{"pid":"aeea3be3065fa2c5cc75dd54f010c387eed5628f","tid":727550,"uid":44559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"尼馬係仆街，應該斷腳"},{"pid":"7c21ff5aa807b201cb9609311f694c80e437bee5","tid":727550,"uid":106675,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36621817_1688405581276393_6502309164469977088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=d67d288aa5b6d3fd678c5f6db5b447f4&amp;oe=5BAA3541\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36621817_168840558